videos.description: Terance Mann gets into the lane and lobs it up for Christ Koumadje, who rises up for the alley-oop finish with the shot clock winding down.
videos.headline: Mann lobs to Koumadje for alley-oop jam

videos.description: Terance Mann drives and dishes to Phil Cofer, who posterizes Wyatt Walker with a huge one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Cofer throws down posterizing dunk
